### Add Version 1.0.0 to Privacy Policy (Active)
POST http://localhost:8085/admin/policies/privacy-policy/versions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "content_html": "<h1>Privacy Policy</h1><p>This is our privacy policy version 1.0.0...</p>",
  "content_markdown": "# Privacy Policy\n\nThis is our privacy policy version 1.0.0...",
  "pdf_url": "https://cdn.example.com/policies/privacy-policy-1.0.0.pdf",
  "is_active": true
}

